                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Iustu <rs key="#Specialized_workers">aurifice</rs> de porta Sancti
                        Gervasii <foreign>vende a</foreign> Urse <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatisse</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">eclesie</rs> Sancte Marie <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> mea
                        quem havire visu sum in loco qui vocitator Casisi, unu caput tenet in <rs
                            key="#Wine">vi[ne]a</rs> Teuderadi, et aliut caput tenet in <rs
                            key="#Wine">vinea</rs> Ansprandi, et de uno latere est de <rs
                            key="#Wine">vinea</rs> Autelm, et de alio latere est de <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs> Faffuli, qui est de sup <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casa</rs> Raduald, qui mihi ex <rs key="#Venditio">comparationem</rs>
                        obvenit de Ildulu, parte mea quantum in ipso loco havire visu sum;
                            <foreign>prezzo</foreign>: auris soledos numero sex boni Lucani stellati
                        expendivilis; <foreign>pena in duplum</foreign>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>:
                        Petrus quamvis indignus <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>. (â€¦) Actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrivono</foreign>: + Iustoni aurifici vindituri; +
                        Sindoin <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> de porta Sancti
                        Vincentii; + Walderamu filio quondam Wattuli; + Autpert <rs
                            key="#Other_clerics">clirico</rs> filio quondam Rotchis.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
